61: /**
62:  * This class acts as a queue that accumulates records into {@link MemoryRecords}
63:  * instances to be sent to the server.
64:  * <p>
65:  * The accumulator uses a bounded amount of memory and append calls will block when that memory is exhausted, unless
66:  * this behavior is explicitly disabled.
67:  */
68: public class RecordAccumulator {
